      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOLLY MISS (2) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including two wins. Placed last time (30.91) at this track in a NG, finishing third and beaten 2.25 lengths. With a clean break looks hard to beat. MULLY THE MASTER (8) has been in super consistent form, last time breaking from this same box when third in a Grade 5 at this track (30.69) and making it three straight placings. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. CHERYL BLUE (6) was a little disappointing last start at Maitland when 5th (25.44) over 450m. Has a strong winning record here at this journey including three wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. One of the main contenders. IMPERIAL AUDREY (1) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.",
